{"tid":1424860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）如何應付警察街頭濫捕？","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:56:27.000Z","uid":225568,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3a5de192df8511e6fc00bf960c74ccd4d495b9","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"如題，想問下大家有咩意見<br />\n 好似今次鐳射槍事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地應該點處理或者點幫？系咪要次次去搞到佢出曬TG/防暴？<br />\n<br />\n選擇：<br />\n<br />\n1a）如果在場的係便衣and無人show委認證，我地即場救唔救人？<br />\n<br />\n1b）便衣/軍裝，有show委任證我地即場救唔救人？<br />\n<br />\n2）警方增援到，想分隔人群，比唔比佢地入去？<br />\n<br />\n3a）最後都系拉左，圍唔圍警署？<br />\n<br />\n3b）圍到放人先散？出煙呢？出防暴？<br />\n<br />\n4）有無其他野可以幫到手？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得今日的情況好大機會再發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，或者大家可以討論定點處理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家提出更多方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876cf95337c83dcddc858fc21178400edbd8926d","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"跪求看法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2a83527f265ed3ec68fde5ee83d6f9f7a82f78","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f665b9d76a6a88cce7338cf7a7b71aaa6ea3f57e","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:46:36.000Z","msg":"希望幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba25a5ee636a7fa4cee0ff9b63fe24029ff5834","tid":1424860,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:47:24.000Z"