s/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d697a2af96776c4ff55e7a40b85e2c7aa42613d","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"好想知其實即刻救人可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac0122695d8640a34b056078d882f2df9d6c3d8","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:02:15.000Z","msg":"或者可以外圍擋住唔比popo入去增援？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efe890196a97e9dda84189b8fd9e007767f09b3","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"最後一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b955e1e61cf1270682a548bb603fadac27d860","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"真最後一推"},{"pid":"2ee6726c468302c55857366e7e91d32c2c3a91f2","tid":1424860,"uid":206705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"推，<br />\n黑警濫捕，白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51720d0871a2dba60fd4feab845164081a208251","tid":1424860,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:12:20.000Z","msg":"依家個政府架構係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>冇辦法能力冇可能</strong></span>制止到警隊做任何嘢<br />\n當政務司司長都俾佢屌返轉頭嘅時候就已經好清楚知道呢個係100%軍政府狀態<br />\n喺政府退讓之前唔該唔好再幻想法律可以對警察作出任何制裁<br />\n一日律政師係佢哋嘅人一日唔會郁到警隊<br />\n一日鄧柄強係二哥一日唔會清算警黑合作<br />\n6月濫用武力警隊冇人需要負責<br />\n有份嘅人仲個個升官發財<br />\n721件事失職嘅警務人員 有份參與同策劃嘅人一個都冇受到製裁<br />\n警察所有對外講話都係大話冚大話<br />\n咁耐以嚟些少法律責任都冇<br />\n點解你會覺得濫捕佢要負責?<br />\n講得衰啲依家佢哋行出嚟用武力夾硬打死幾個前線都冇人可以喺法律上有能制裁佢哋<br />\n除咗解放軍<br />\n呢啲就係軍警政權<br />\n<br />\n要對付警隊根本只能夠用經濟/國際制裁方法逼政府解散行政班底<br />\n但係到時黑警一定會反撲<br />\n因為知道陽壽已盡<br />\n呢個係非焦土唯一方向"},{"pid":"3fc848e321ce2cb6512fa740970653979a78672d","tid":1424860,"uid":141197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:33:39.000Z","msg":"試下旅遊區快閃<br />\n夜晚老蘭山頂嗰啲<br />\nd狗tg埋鬼佬等外國勢力介入"},{"pid":"df6bab415a28c08c100a76a3d5b84ecb343503a1","tid":1424860,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:34:24.000Z","msg":"濫捕囉 全部街坊"},{"pid":"9ab1b9e6038710d4a31d0b720ce866fda78d4e1a","tid":1424860,"uid":28524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"真係要搵人俾專業意見，咁樣俾人拉，我真係睇到好撚心痛，又好撚嬲，就快谷到想自殘，因為真係好撚忟呀！屌你老母"},{"pid":"21f1eec4c8a2d39f224e31c0fcb0a56f3ce2bd7b","tid":1424860,"uid":271431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:40:36.000Z","msg":"便衣無委任証 可能係公安or黑社會都唔定..<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77df041b547d634e3297d5a519691a796ba9b6a0","tid":1424860,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"876cf95337c83dcddc858fc21178400edbd8926d","tid":1424860,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"跪求看法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:42:40.000Z","msg":"見到班防暴做埋畜蟲既野，就諗起自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425253</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n物理上就哩個po  精神上就真係要熟讀通例 清楚自己權利同狗既權限"}]}